text: Los Navegantes (; roughly translated as Los Navegantes Neighborhood) is a residential neighbourhood in the south-east of Pichilemu, Chile. It is near the Municipal Stadium and La Cruz Hill. Los Navegantes has a perimeter of approximately . It was founded between 1996-1997. It has a court. The Pichilemu tsunami secure side, starts near the neighborhood.TERREMOTO DE LARGA DURACIÓN E INTENSIDAD AFECTÓ AL 80% DEL PAÍS EN HORAS DE LA MADRUGADA , Pichilemu News. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Pichilemu Category:Neighborhoods Category:Settlements in Chile
